description:
Repost from @chasingsunsetsllc

Lone Bandit - Camera Harness: Dark Brown Colorway | 8-9oz Leather | Contoured, seamless shoulder design | Adjustable strap length | Solid brass hardware | Link in bio to shop now

{8}

#photography #photographyforbeginners #cameragear 

@brevite sent me a camera bag to test out and review almost 3 years ago, and yeah, I'm just now getting to putting out this video. But I've been using their Jumper camera backpack the entire time; it's my EDC and most often my go-to travel camera backpack. I just recently spent a week in Puerto Rico and this was the camera bag I rolled with; in this video I'm showing everything I took on the trip and giving my thoughts on the Jumper backpack.

The Jumper (2026 Edition)
https://brevite.co/products/the-jumper-photo-2-0

